{"title":"Hexo生成github page","date":"2020-04-28T21:24:32.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 29, 2020","L":"04/29/2020","MM-DD":"04-29"},"link":"2020/04/29/hexo-generate-github-page","tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2020-05-17T04:16:51.428Z","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"前期准备\">前期准备<a title=\"#前期准备\" href=\"#前期准备\"></a></h2>\n<p>要使用hexo，首先你需要检测电脑上是否已经安装下列应用程序：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/\" title=\"Node\" target=\"_blank\">Node.js</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\" title=\"Git\" target=\"_blank\">Git</a></p>\n<!-- ，如果你的计算机上已经安装了它们，那么可以[跳过这一步](#quick-start)。 -->\n<p>如果已经安装上述必备程序，那么接下来只需要使用 npm 即可完成 Hexo 的安装。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"quick-start\">Quick Start<a title=\"#quick-start\" href=\"#quick-start\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"initial-project\">Initial project<a title=\"#initial-project\" href=\"#initial-project\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-new-post\">Create a new post<a title=\"#create-a-new-post\" href=\"#create-a-new-post\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"run-server\">Run server<a title=\"#run-server\" href=\"#run-server\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\">Server</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"deploy\">Deploy<a title=\"#deploy\" href=\"#deploy\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"install-git-deploy-plugin\">Install git deploy plugin<a title=\"#install-git-deploy-plugin\" href=\"#install-git-deploy-plugin\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"configure\">Configure<a title=\"#configure\" href=\"#configure\"></a></h3>\n<p>open file “_config.yml” in the project at first level, and configure deploy node.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">type</span>: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">repo: git url</span><br><span class=\"line\">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"clean-browser-cache\">Clean browser cache<a title=\"#clean-browser-cache\" href=\"#clean-browser-cache\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"generate-static-files\">Generate static files<a title=\"#generate-static-files\" href=\"#generate-static-files\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites<a title=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\" href=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\">Deployment</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>There is no details about github page configure, about more info please google.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"releated-links\">Releated Links<a title=\"#releated-links\" href=\"#releated-links\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/46096258\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub Page+Hexo+nexT 搭建个人博客</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Docker安装kafka","link":"2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka"},"next":{"title":"世界上的另一个我","link":"2019/04/29/another-me-in-the-world"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/04/29/hexo-generate-github-page/","toc":[{"id":"前期准备","title":"前期准备","index":"1"},{"id":"quick-start","title":"Quick Start","index":"2","children":[{"id":"initial-project","title":"Initial project","index":"2.1"},{"id":"create-a-new-post","title":"Create a new post","index":"2.2"},{"id":"run-server","title":"Run server","index":"2.3"}]},{"id":"deploy","title":"Deploy","index":"3","children":[{"id":"install-git-deploy-plugin","title":"Install git deploy plugin","index":"3.1"},{"id":"configure","title":"Configure","index":"3.2"},{"id":"clean-browser-cache","title":"Clean browser cache","index":"3.3"},{"id":"generate-static-files","title":"Generate static files","index":"3.4"},{"id":"deploy-to-remote-sites","title":"Deploy to remote sites","index":"3.5"}]},{"id":"releated-links","title":"Releated Links","index":"4"}],"reward":true}